Quickstrike:





Quickstrike froze as Black Arachnia left him with the duty with 
computer work. And with something that sounded like he had to be an 
engineering bot to do. He wasn't like that. He looked around, then 
bolted after Black Arachnia.

"Hey surgar-bot, wait up! Uuh, listen what ah did back there wit' th' 
ship, it was more like common sense than uh skill. Ah ain't that good 
wit' doin' uh job like that. Can we go explorin'? Dark Mouse has good 
skills on computers." He grinned, trying to get on her good side.
